__NAME__ purpose
set the current shopping cart
__END__


__NAME__ see also
delete_cart
__END__


__NAME__ synopsis
<row>
	<entry>
		<group>
			<arg choice='plain'>nickname</arg>
			<arg choice='plain'>name</arg>
		</group>
	</entry>
	<entry>Yes</entry><entry>Yes</entry>
	<entry></entry>
	<entry>Cart name to switch to.</entry>
</row>
&TAG_NON_CONTAINER;
__END__


__NAME__ description
This simple tag sets the default cart name for tags that operate on it
(such as
<tag>shipping</tag>,
<tag>price</tag>,
<tag>total</tag>,
<tag>subtotal</tag> or
<tag>nitems</tag>).
__END__

__NAME__ notes
See the &glos-cart; glossary entry.
__END__

__NAME__ example: Set new default cart name
Place the following on an Interchange page:
<programlisting>
[cart NEW]
</programlisting>
__END__

__NAME__ see also
__END__
